        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3379",
        "content": "I do not scruple to tell you, that I am unhappy, and that the watch of the last night has not assisted me to discover Ludovico; upon every occurrence of the night you must excuse my reserve.'",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
