        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3379",
        "content": "In the evening, the Count called, as he had promised, at the convent, and Emily was surprised to perceive a mixture of playful ridicule and of reserve in his mention of the north apartment.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
