        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3379",
        "content": "At first, she was frantic and melancholy by quick alternatives; then, she sunk into a deep and settled melancholy, which still, however, has, at times, been interrupted by fits of wildness, and, of late, these have again been frequent.'",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
