        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3379",
        "content": "Emily did not appear to notice this question, but remained thoughtful, for a few moments, and then said, 'It was about that same period that the Marchioness de Villeroi expired.'",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
