        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3379",
        "content": "'I do not doubt it,' replied the Count, 'and I will not deny myself and Blanche the pleasure of visiting you, if your affairs should allow you to be at La Vallee, about the time when we can meet you there.'",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
