        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3379",
        "content": "'Her death presents to us a great and awful lesson,' continued the abbess; 'let us read it, and profit by it; let it teach us to prepare ourselves for the change, that awaits us all!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
