        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3379",
        "content": "When she had finished, she returned the miniature to Emily. 'Keep it,' said she, 'I bequeath it to you, for I must believe it is your right.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
