        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3379",
        "content": "I tasted too what was called the sweet of revenge-but it was transient, it expired even with the object, that provoked it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
